<section props="page-margin-footer:0.5in; page-margin-header:0.5in">
<p style="Heading 1">Mail Merge Tool</p>
<p style="Normal"><c></c>This dialog is a standard Open File dialog. However, instead of looking for AbiWord files, it looks for mail merge data source files. When you open a file in this dialog, the information from the mail merge source is inserted in the appropriate mail merge fields in your document.</p>
<p style="Heading 2"><c></c>Cancel</p>
<p style="Normal">Closes the dialog without performing any action.</p>
<p style="Heading 2"><c></c>OK</p>
<p style="Normal">Merge the data source with your document</p>
</section>
